    "This method focuses on multi-path programs, which are more realistic and challenging to analyze than single-path programs.",
    "The authors highlight the benefits of using MBPTA over SPTA, emphasizing its practicality and lower requirement for detailed hardware knowledge.",
    "The results demonstrate that their EVT-based MBPTA method can produce reliable pWCET estimates with less than 15% pessimism compared to the tightest bounds obtainable by any PTA technique.",
    "The authors also discussed the necessary statistical properties and experimental setup required to ensure the sound application of EVT to WCET analysis.When execution time observations are not i.i.d., EVT can still be applied if they exhibit stationarity or weak dependencies.",
    "EVT and Observations with Dependencies category extends EVT application to dependent observations."
